itedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:02:44.000Z","msg":"呢幾十億肯定加埋市長省長條數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e191c1eda010b6b439bee272db901514801904d","tid":669603,"uid":17266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:06:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個地方小官貪到幾十億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62b546fb0906efff48e1e10e1eb04d9a620f4f24","tid":669603,"uid":26218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:11:18.000Z","msg":"然後咪落黎炒貴曬香港啲樓囉屌你老母"},{"pid":"d258b3440520970bf6bac9f512f3fda2541dcfa9","tid":669603,"uid":143288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"應該計少左個零"},{"pid":"63f8c01bec9d0938355a78e4a7a048defb3ae987","tid":669603,"uid":123738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:39:35.000Z","msg":"市長震驚點解過自己手既少過432億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中央震驚堂堂支那大國，竟然一個地方咁撚少錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a25e12d0d8a0387285723631034c09095113e3e","tid":669603,"uid":44184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-19T07:46:03.000Z","msg":"又贏!!"},{"pid":"baa769d895ce5b775c216d7cfb2b4487325e274e","tid":669603,"uid":103954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c